### Fetch all tasks

GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### Stream tasks

GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/stream HTTP/2.0

### Create a new task

POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Yotei task 2024/07/01",
    "children": []
}

### Create a new task with a child

POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Task with child",
    "children": ["bfc6e552-c5d4-4617-b8c6-5cae0617f64f"]
}

### Update a task with a child

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "6f98a57c-0ccc-4551-a1c9-e528eefd7252",
    "name": "I'm a task",
    "children": [
        "bfc6e552-c5d4-4617-b8c6-5cae0617f64f", 
        "9b8e71c1-7a59-471e-81e9-6a184bb1503a", 
        "cc26825b-921f-47d9-8233-bc305390e826",
        "30d70aaa-3155-4250-b021-ff82ea2c6227",
        "86c93019-2bf4-447d-a55d-da447e6b954e"
    ]
}

### Update a task with a child

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
